{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-js","path":"/post/board-game-tabletop-game-perkembangan/","result":{"data":{"wordpressPost":{"title":"Tabletop Game, Board Game, dan Perkembangannya Selama Ini","content":"<p>Jauh sebelum video game ataupun permainan berbasis tenaga listrik populer dan menguasai populasi dunia, permainan yang dilakukan oleh manusia kebanyakan berupa permainan yang memanfaatkan aktivitas fisik. Serta permainan yang menggunakan pemikiran otak atau adu strategi.</p>\n<p><strong>Baca Juga: <a href=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/gaming-dengan-home-console-vs-gaming-dengan-pc-pilih-yang-mana/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Gaming Dengan Home Console vs Gaming Dengan PC, Pilih yang Mana?</a></strong></p>\n<p>Hal-hal semacam itu yang menjadi sarana permainan manusia sebelum era permainan elektronik (baik video game maupun permainan elektronik mewah seperti <em>quadcopter / drones</em> muncul dan mendominasi arena bermain di kehidupan sosial manusia modern.</p>\n<p><strong>Baca Juga: <a href=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/trend-drone-quadcopter-mainan-mahal-yang-prestisius-ada-lomba-balapannya-loh/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Trend Drone Quadcopter, Mainan Mahal Yang Prestisius. Ada Lomba Balapannya Loh!</a></strong></p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_49807\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-49807\" data-attachment-id=\"49807\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/board-game-tabletop-game-perkembangan/attachment/01-tabletop-game/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/01-tabletop-game.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"01-tabletop-game\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/01-tabletop-game-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/01-tabletop-game.jpg\" class=\"wp-image-49807 size-full\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/01-tabletop-game.jpg\" alt=\"drone\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/01-tabletop-game.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/01-tabletop-game-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-49807\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Permainan era modern berbasis elektronik. Sumber: FromWhereIdrone</p></div></p>\n<p>Permainan sebelum era modern tersebut lazim dikategorikan sebagai “Board / Tabletop Game”. Alias permainan yang dimainkan di atas sebuah permukaan meja. Dan jika dilihat dari popularitas, game jenis ini yang paling populer dan gampang untuk dikenali sepertinya adalah “Catur / Chess”.</p>\n<h2>Catur, Tabletop Game Lintas Usia</h2>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_49808\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-49808\" data-attachment-id=\"49808\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/board-game-tabletop-game-perkembangan/attachment/02-tabletop-game/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/02-tabletop-game.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"02-tabletop-game\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/02-tabletop-game-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/02-tabletop-game.jpg\" class=\"wp-image-49808 size-full\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/02-tabletop-game.jpg\" alt=\"tabletop game catur lipat\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/02-tabletop-game.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/02-tabletop-game-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-49808\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Board / Tabletop Game paling populer di dunia? Sumber: MEC</p></div></p>\n<p>Rasanya mustahil kalau ada yang tidak mengenal permainan Catur.</p>\n<p>Permainan dengan menggunakan permukaan 64 kotak dalam format baris 8&#215;8 ini di-klaim berasal dari India sejak abad ke-7 Masehi sebelum kemudian memasuki wilayah Eropa pada abad ke-9 dan akhirnya memiliki standarisasi aturan permainan di abad ke-19.</p>\n<p>Dengan format “16 versus 16” di atas papan hitam putih kotak-kotak, permainan Catur menuntut fokus dan pemikiran strategis dari dua pihak yang bertempur adu taktik di atas papan. Kemenangan diraih saat Raja/King dari pihak lawan berhasil direbut. Jika itu terjadi maka permainan berakhir.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_49809\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-49809\" data-attachment-id=\"49809\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/board-game-tabletop-game-perkembangan/attachment/03-tabletop-game/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/03-tabletop-game.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"03-tabletop-game\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/03-tabletop-game-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/03-tabletop-game.jpg\" class=\"wp-image-49809 size-full\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/03-tabletop-game.jpg\" alt=\"tabletop game catur\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/03-tabletop-game.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/03-tabletop-game-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-49809\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Digemari segala kelompok umur dan gender. Sumber: FactorDaily</p></div></p>\n<p>Dalam kasus spesial, kemenangan tidak dapat dicapai sehingga menghasilkan “remis” atau <em>draw</em>/imbang. Hal ini menunjukkan kalau dalam permainan Catur, kemenangan tidak berarti sebuah kondisi yang pasti akan tercapai. Perlu strategi dan kemampuan deduksi tinggi agar dapat memenangkan permainan Catur.</p>\n<h2>Go: Catur Jepang Berseni Tinggi</h2>\n<p>Tentu tidak hanya Catur yang ada dan populer sebagai Board / Tabletop Game. Ada juga misalnya “Go” yang berasal dari negara Jepang.</p>\n<p>Serunya lagi, Go bahkan sempat dijadikan tema untuk manga/anime “Hikaru no Go” (1999 &#8211; 2003). Mungkin tujuannya agar permainan Go ini juga bisa digemari kalangan muda penikmat manga/anime? Karena permainan Go secara tradisional lebih banyak digemari kalangan usia dewasa/tua di Jepang.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_49810\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-49810\" data-attachment-id=\"49810\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/board-game-tabletop-game-perkembangan/attachment/04-tabletop-game/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/04-tabletop-game.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"04-tabletop-game\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/04-tabletop-game-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/04-tabletop-game.jpg\" class=\"wp-image-49810 size-full\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/04-tabletop-game.jpg\" alt=\"tabletop game hikaru no go\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/04-tabletop-game.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/04-tabletop-game-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-49810\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Hikaru no go. Sumber: Hulu</p></div></p>\n<p>Permainan Go sendiri mirip dengan Catur namun dengan peraturan yang berbeda dan bidak berbeda pula.</p>\n<p>Jika tujuan catur adalah mengalahkan Raja/King maka Go bertujuan menguasai area permainan/teritori dari lawan. Permainan Go dipercaya berasal dari daratan China sejak 2.500 tahun yang lalu dan banyak dimainkan di wilayah-wilayah Asia Timur.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_49811\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-49811\" data-attachment-id=\"49811\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/board-game-tabletop-game-perkembangan/attachment/05-tabletop-game/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/05-tabletop-game.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"05-tabletop-game\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/05-tabletop-game-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/05-tabletop-game.jpg\" class=\"wp-image-49811 size-full\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/05-tabletop-game.jpg\" alt=\"tabletop game go\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/05-tabletop-game.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/05-tabletop-game-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-49811\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Bidang permainan Go. Sumber: Wired</p></div></p>\n<h2>Dungeons &amp; Dragons: Board Game Rumit Tapi Asyik</h2>\n<p>Lantas bagaimana dengan Board / Tabletop di era modern? Dalam artian tercipta di era abad kini?</p>\n<p>Ada yang namanya “Dungeons &amp; Dragons” atau sering disingkat dengan D&amp;D / DnD. Game Board / Tabletop ini diciptakan oleh Gary Gygax dan Dave Arneson pada tahun 1974. Dengan genre ‘Fantasy Tabletop Role-Playing Game’ berbasis narasi, D&amp;D terus bertahan dan jadi salah satu permainan Board / Tabletop terkenal di dunia hingga hari ini.</p>\n<p>Dungeons and Dragons bahkan dianggap sebagai nenek moyang game-game Role Playing di era modern; termasuk yang menggunakan platform video game.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_49812\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-49812\" data-attachment-id=\"49812\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/board-game-tabletop-game-perkembangan/attachment/06-tabletop-game/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/06-tabletop-game.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"06-tabletop-game\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/06-tabletop-game-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/06-tabletop-game.jpg\" class=\"wp-image-49812 size-full\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/06-tabletop-game.jpg\" alt=\"tabletop game dnd\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/06-tabletop-game.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/06-tabletop-game-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-49812\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Set original “Dungeons &amp; Dragons” tahun 1974. Kini harganya selangit! Sumber: Behance</p></div></p>\n<p>Di tahun 1977, D&amp;D mengalami separasi dan menjadi dua produk: “Dungeons &amp; Dragons” dengan aturan bermain klasik seperti saat diciptakan oleh Gygax dan Arneson serta “Advanced Dungeons &amp; Dragons” (atau disingkat AD&amp;D) yang lebih terstruktur dengan peraturan yang lebih ketat serta kompleks jika dibandingkan dengan D&amp;D. Namun kedua game pada prinsipnya merupakan game yang sama.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_49813\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-49813\" data-attachment-id=\"49813\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/board-game-tabletop-game-perkembangan/attachment/07-tabletop-game/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/07-tabletop-game.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"07-tabletop-game\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/07-tabletop-game-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/07-tabletop-game.jpg\" class=\"wp-image-49813 size-full\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/07-tabletop-game.jpg\" alt=\"tabletop game advanced dnd\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/07-tabletop-game.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/07-tabletop-game-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-49813\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Buku manual resmi AD&amp;D. Sumber: 2WarpsToNeptune</p></div></p>\n<p>Ingat serial TV horor Netflix “Stanger Things”? Di episode awal Season One terlihat anak-anak itu sedang bermain “Dungeons &amp; Dragons”. Kira-kira seperti itulah cara bermain Board / Tabletop D&amp;D.</p>\n<p><strong>Baca Juga: <a href=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/stranger-things-serial-netflix-tentang-dunia-lain-yang-menegangkan/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Stranger Things &#8211; Serial Netflix Tentang Dunia Lain Yang Menegangkan</a></strong></p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_49814\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-49814\" data-attachment-id=\"49814\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/board-game-tabletop-game-perkembangan/attachment/08-tabletop-game/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/08-tabletop-game.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"08-tabletop-game\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/08-tabletop-game-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/08-tabletop-game.jpg\" class=\"wp-image-49814 size-full\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/08-tabletop-game.jpg\" alt=\"tabletop game stranger things\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/08-tabletop-game.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/08-tabletop-game-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-49814\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Serunya bermain D&amp;D di tahun ‘80an. Sumber: TheNewYorkTimes</p></div></p>\n<p><em>Fun Fact:</em> Capcom pernah menciptakan dua video game arcade D&amp;D dengan setting “Mystara Campaign” ber-genre Action Adventure. Game-game ini berjudul “Dungeons &amp; Dragons: Tower of Doom” (1993) dan “Dungeons &amp; Dragons: Shadow over Mystara” (1996). Pemain arcade era ‘90an hampir pasti mengenali ataupun pernah memainkan kedua game ini.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_49815\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-49815\" data-attachment-id=\"49815\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/board-game-tabletop-game-perkembangan/attachment/09-tabletop-game/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/09-tabletop-game.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"09-tabletop-game\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/09-tabletop-game-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/09-tabletop-game.jpg\" class=\"wp-image-49815 size-full\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/09-tabletop-game.jpg\" alt=\"tabletop game dnd arcade\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/09-tabletop-game.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/09-tabletop-game-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-49815\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Versi Game Arcade dari Board / Tabletop Game. Sumber: YouTube</p></div></p>\n<h2>Berbagai Macam Board Game</h2>\n<p>Selain game-game yang memang diciptakan dengan tujuan dimainkan di atas meja seperti “Ular Tangga” ataupun “Ludo” (orang Indonesia pasti tahu kedua Board / Tabletop Games ini), ada pula Board / Tabletop Games yang dibuat berdasarkan <em>pop icon</em> populer, seperti misalnya Board Game “Star Wars” atau malah Board Game dari video game seperti “Resident Evil”.</p>\n<p>Hal ini untuk mengakomodasi penonton film ataupun pemain video game yang ingin bermain secara beramai-ramai dengan format Board / Tabletop Game.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_49816\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-49816\" data-attachment-id=\"49816\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/board-game-tabletop-game-perkembangan/attachment/10-tabletop-game/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/10-tabletop-game.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"10-tabletop-game\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/10-tabletop-game-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/10-tabletop-game.jpg\" class=\"wp-image-49816 size-full\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/10-tabletop-game.jpg\" alt=\"tabletop game resident evil\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/10-tabletop-game.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/10-tabletop-game-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-49816\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Keren! Board Game dari video game horor. Sumber: Polygon</p></div></p>\n<p>Jadi pada akhirnya, Board / Tabletop Games tidak akan musnah atau tergeser jenis permainan lain karena game model ini sudah terbukti ketangguhannya bertahan di kehidupan sosial masyarakat selama ribuan tahun.</p>\n<p>Board / Tabletop Games akan ber-evolusi, berkembang dan menyesuaikan diri dengan waktu serta era namun mereka tidak akan pernah benar-benar menghilang dari kehidupan sosial masyarakat.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_49817\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-49817\" data-attachment-id=\"49817\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/board-game-tabletop-game-perkembangan/attachment/11-tabletop-game/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/11-tabletop-game.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&qu